         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>All Friendly Enough Expression Language (FEEL) expressions that you use in your boxed expressions must conform to the FEEL syntax requirements in the OMG <xref href="https://www.omg.org/spec/DMN" scope="external">Decision Model and Notation specification</xref>.</p>
